description.en: SHARES is a masternode and PoS coin whose usecase platform will enable the conversion and monetization of blockchain projects into publicly quoted and tradeable equity. Blockchain projects usecases are collaterized and converted to a crypto digital pseudo-stock to be quoted and traded as equity shares on the Cryptoshares platform/network.
